Hello everyone,
I was trying to get the NodeSDK running for my vagrant setup following the documentation here <https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric/blob/131b36c9fce40447735fa497e5bdfa8fa3eb3536/docs/nodeSDK/app-developer-env-setup.mdHowever> the first `make all` command failed with `SyntaxError: Unexpected token =>` on the arrow operator. Any idea what's missing here?
